quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  45,27,"Woodanii Alla laamu kammuuji e leydi, ñande darnga darii ñande heen meerenteeɓe perta"
  45,28,"Haɗa yiya -aan nulaaɗa- kala lenyol na gurfanii e koppi mum,kala lenyol na noddiree deftere mum hannde woni ko njoɓeteɗon ko ngollatnaɗon e nder aduna"
  45,29,"Ndee ko deftere amen honde wowla goonga, Min ngoniina Min ceeraani wonde emin njamira nde winndate ko ngollatna ɗon"
  45,30,"Tawi ko ɓeen goonɗinɓe ɓe ngolli golle lobbe O naatnatɓe e yurmeende makko, ko ɗuum woni mala ɓanngungal"
  45,31,Tawi ko ɓeen heefareeɓe mbela aayeeje Am ɗe njanngetanooke e dow mon mawnikiniɗo laatiɗon yimɓe bonɓe
  45,32,"Sibɓe wiyaama pellet fodoore Alla ko goonga sikke alah heen mbi*on min nganndah ko woni darnga, min cikkiti cikkitagol min ngonaani yananaaɓe"
  45,33,"boneeji ɗi ɓe faggitinoo ɗin feñana ɓe, ko ɓe jalkitaynoo kon fiiltoo ɓe"
  45,34,"ɓe wi*ana hannde Min njejjita mon hono no njejjitirɗon pottal ñalngu mon hannde ngu, ko yiite woni hoɗorde mno on ndanyatah walladiiɓe"
  45,35,"ɗuum noon ko sabu on njaggarii aayeeje Alla ɗe jalkito nguurndam aduna hoomti on,hannde ɓe njaltatah e yiite ɓe nduttataaka aduna ɓe golla golle lobbe haa Alla weleeɓe"
  45,36,Woodanii Alla yettoore nder kammuuji e leydi Jom binnde
  45,37,Na woodani Mbo manngu nder kammuuji e leydi ko kanko woni mbo gooto foolah ñeeñuɗo